    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Interest-bearing certificates of public or private debt, usually offered in series, constituting promises to pay the lender a certain amount of money at a fixed future date.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
